      "translation_en": "Yesterday was very cold, I wore a jacket, but my mood was very happy.",
      "translation_ko": "어제는 매우 추워서 외투를 입었지만 기분은 매우 즐거웠어요."
    },
    {
      "text": "下雨天路很滑，要小心，可是天氣很涼快。",
      "pinyin": "Xiàyǔ tiān lù hěn huá, yào xiǎoxīn, kěshì tiānqì hěn liángkuài.",
      "pinyin_numeric": "xia4yu3 tian1 lu4 hen3 hua2, yao4 xiao3xin1, ke3shi4 tian1qi4 hen3 liang2kuai4.",
      "translation_en": "Rainy weather makes the roads very slippery, so be careful, but the weather is very cool.",
      "translation_ko": "비 오는 날씨에 길이 매우 미끄러우니 조심해야 하지만 날씨는 매우 시원해요."
    }
  ]
